2:T712,{"@context":"https://schema.org","@type":"FAQPage","mainEntity":[{"@type":"Question","name":"Is SE Ranking better than Semrush?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"It depends on your needs. SE Ranking scores 8.0 overall while Semrush scores 9.0. SE Ranking is best for small agencies and freelancers, while Semrush excels for SEO professionals and digital agencies."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Which is cheaper, SE Ranking or Semrush?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"SE Ranking starts at $65/mo and Semrush starts at $139.95/mo.   Overall value depends on which features you need."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Can I switch from SE Ranking to Semrush?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Yes, most users can migrate between these platforms. Both SE Ranking and Semrush support data import/export. The migration process typically involves exporting your data from one platform and importing it into the other. Some tools also offer migration assistance to make the transition smoother."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"What do users say about SE Ranking vs Semrush?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"On review platforms, SE Ranking holds an overall rating of 8/10 and an ease of use score of 7/10. Semrush has an overall rating of 9/10 and ease of use score of 7/10. Users praise SE Ranking for excellent value for an all-in-one tool and Semrush for most comprehensive seo toolkit available."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Which should I choose in 2026, SE Ranking or Semrush?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"In 2026, we recommend Semrush for most users based on its overall score and feature set. However, SE Ranking remains a strong contender, especially if you prioritize excellent value for an all-in-one tool. Try both free trials before committing."}}]}0:{"buildId":"P2JZirFppjRTCRUsq6bTg","rsc":["$","$1","c",{"children":[[["$","script",null,{"type":"application/ld+json","dangerouslySetInnerHTML":{"__html":"$2"}}],["$","div",null,{"c